<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<manifest xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android" android:versionCode="22" android:versionName="3.4.2" package="net.gotev.uploadservicedemo">
	<uses-sdk android:minSdkVersion="16" android:targetSdkVersion="26" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.WAKE_LOCK" />
	<application android:theme="resourceId:0x7f0f0006" android:label="Upload Service" android:icon="res/mipmap-mdpi-v4/ic_launcher.png" android:name="net.gotev.uploadservicedemo.App" android:allowBackup="true" android:supportsRtl="true">
		<provider android:name="android.support.v4.content.FileProvider" android:exported="false" android:authorities="net.gotev.uploadservicedemo.provider" android:grantUriPermissions="true">
			<meta-data android:name="android.support.FILE_PROVIDER_PATHS" android:resource="res/xml/nnf_provider_paths.xml" />
		</provider>
		<receiver android:name="net.gotev.uploadservicedemo.events.UploadReceiver" android:exported="false">
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="net.gotev.uploadservicedemo.uploadservice.broadcast.status" />
			</intent-filter>
		</receiver>
		<receiver android:name="net.gotev.uploadservicedemo.events.NotificationActionsReceiver" android:exported="false">
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="net.gotev.uploadservicedemo.notification.action" />
			</intent-filter>
		</receiver>
		<activity android:theme="resourceId:0x7f0f00ab" android:label="Upload Service" android:name="com.nononsenseapps.filepicker.FilePickerActivity">
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="android.intent.action.GET_CONTENT" />
				<category android:name="android.intent.category.DEFAULT" />
			</intent-filter>
		</activity>
		<activity android:label="Upload Service" android:name="net.gotev.uploadservicedemo.MainActivity" android:launchMode="singleTask">
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="android.intent.action.MAIN" />
				<category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER" />
			</intent-filter>
		</activity>
		<activity android:label="Multipart Upload" android:name="net.gotev.uploadservicedemo.MultipartUploadActivity" android:launchMode="singleTask" android:parentActivityName="net.gotev.uploadservicedemo.MainActivity" />
		<activity android:label="Binary Upload" android:name="net.gotev.uploadservicedemo.BinaryUploadActivity" android:launchMode="singleTask" android:parentActivityName="net.gotev.uploadservicedemo.MainActivity" />
		<activity android:label="FTP Upload" android:name="net.gotev.uploadservicedemo.FTPUploadActivity" android:launchMode="singleTask" android:parentActivityName="net.gotev.uploadservicedemo.MainActivity" />
		<activity android:theme="resourceId:0x7f0f00ab" android:label="Select file to upload" android:name="net.gotev.uploadservicedemo.utils.BackHandlingFilePickerActivity">
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="android.intent.action.GET_CONTENT" />
				<category android:name="android.intent.category.DEFAULT" />
			</intent-filter>
		</activity>
		<service android:name="net.gotev.uploadservice.UploadService" android:enabled="true" android:exported="false" />
	</application>
</manifest>
